Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:44.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:49.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:54.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:59.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:20.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:30.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:37.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:43.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:50.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.18,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.10,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:44.23,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:49.45,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:54.20,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:59.16,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.46,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.84,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.05,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.67,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.34,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:20.18,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:30.11,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:37.49,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:43.62,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:50.55,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.43,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,IN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:19:01.83,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.1}憧れ続けた　光に包まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:08.25,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.1}初めて気付いたの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:14.76,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.1}傷跡だらけの心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:21.52,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.1}明日を恐れ　流した涙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:27.69,IN-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.1}言い訳ばかりの日々はもう…
